it's only tested to build on linux and i don't really care enough to try it on macos or anything

uhhh so its pretty simple controls:
 - WASD for movement mostly
 - space to fly up
 - shift to fly down
 - right click to break blocks
 - left click to place blocks
 - scroll or numbers to select slot in hotbar
